Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好強 但要是僅僅交手一回合就放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼自己也不配稱為劍士了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只有在那個世界 我才是一個劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她能看見「四重痛楚」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(345,422)}Quadruple Pain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼能就這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,被妳打倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是「絕劍」的十一連擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,「原創劍技」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(320,422)}OSS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果敗在這樣的劍技之下...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒什麼遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就決定是這位姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什...咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那、那個 決鬥的勝負呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,戰到這裡我已經很滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說姐姐妳想戰到最後？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在找能讓我有感覺的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,現在終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 亞絲娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,亞絲娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託妳了 請妳務必要助我們一臂之力！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,助你們...一臂之力？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.19,0:23:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,次回 沉睡騎士
